0.1.2.name: connect20/Cre_Cresecure
0.1.2.description: CRE Secure Hosted Payment Page (HPP) provides you with the benefits of credit card processing without credit card security liabilities or Payment Card Industry (PCI-DSS) security costs. That’s because HPP is the only PCI-certified payment system that seamlessly connects your existing shopping cart program to the major banks and processors.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
